settings.description: Not a Rip-off of an existing series called "The 8 Worlds" I swear. This is desert plains, with a TON of coins to collect.
watch out! boomerang bros are known to guard precious treasure in this long not so dangerous bridge!
Well, the objective is stupidly simple. Find the right level and don't do all that hard work for nothing! P-Wing included for special time wasting! Careful as something may block your path.
Magic Blocks, are on Buster Beetle Room, also Room 4 is Bonus Room, so Enjoy!
